name: Banana Baked French Toast Recipe | Shireen Anwar | Masala TV
ingredients: Ingredients for Banana Baked French Toast Recipe: Bread Slices 4 Eggs 3 Milk 1-½ cup Sugar 4 tbsp Vanilla Essence ½ tsp Bananas (sliced) 4
instructions: Beat together eggs, sugar, vanilla essence. Put bread slices in a Pyrex dish. Spread with beaten egg mixture topped with sliced bananas. Bake in a pre heated oven until 20 mins will set. Banana Baked French Toast ready to serve.
